      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "敲门而入的龙骑兵鞠了一个标准的90度躬，然后看向这边",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 601020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "如，如果打扰到扎拉阁下和指挥官工作的话，万分抱歉！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "有什么事情吗？",
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 601020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "那个……其，其实属下是来向扎拉阁下道谢的。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 601020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "多亏了扎拉阁下上次的建议，属下和她们玩得很开心，也交到了新的朋友！实在是非常感谢！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "妳是说上次那件事吗？哎呀，我不是说过了吗，只是举手之劳而已。同伴之间，不需要那么客套的。还有，叫我扎拉就好了呢",
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 601020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "哪里的事！扎拉阁下明明特地带我去服装店一件一件的挑选——",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "随便打扰指挥官的工作可是不好的行为哦？如果是和舰队事务无关的话题，我想回去之后再说比较好吧",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 601020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "非，非常对不起！",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "龙骑兵一路倒退到了办公室的门口，又鞠了个躬，然后从外面把门轻轻地关上了。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 1,
      "say": "没想到那孩子连道谢都如此执着",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "expression": 2,
      "say": "嗯？指挥官是对我刚刚和她说的事情感兴趣吗？随便深究少女的秘密可不是绅士的行为哦？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "呵呵，其实也不是什么特别神秘的事情",
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "龙骑兵她不太擅长和人交往。最近好不容易交到了别的阵营的朋友，结果在一起约好出去玩之后，对自己要穿的服装烦恼了起来。",
      "actor": 603020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
